{
  "stem": "15174.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But I remember my parents and I standing [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] on the deck looking at the pier getting smaller and smaller in the distance, and I remember my father crying, and he's-- and I remember his saying to my mother, you know, all our relatives who are in Poland, God only knows when or if we'll ever see them again.",
      "word_count": 62
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And of course, we never did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They were all killed in the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But anyway, soon we were on the open sea.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And suddenly we were in this new world.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, it was-- it was incredible, because apparently the-- the-- I've read about this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I didn't know about it at the time, but the-- the captain of the ship, a guy named Schroeder, was really a pretty good guy.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he had told the crew that he was-- that they were to treat us as if we were regular passengers on this cruise ship, even though we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so suddenly these German waiters and sailors were polite to us, and they were-- treated us like human beings.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was such a change from what had been going on in Germany itself.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It was-- it was, really, it was surreal.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It was really-- it was surreal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At first, it was difficult to get used to.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And, of course, you know, it was a beautiful ship, I guess.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I think the ship had been commissioned less than 10 years before that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So it was a new ship.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was a cruise ship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "It was very nice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I remember the dining room.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You know, it was a large dining room.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We were-- we traveled certainly not in first class or second class.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I guess we were in third class.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
